  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he jumped out of the car, and he came to us and he asked us what-- what are we doing here?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I told him-- because I was the head of the group-- I told him that we-- this is the last day that we are coming back from work because we couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are a small group, and that we are waiting to get in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The he asked us, and I was afraid of the question, what do we have in all these packages?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, I-- I told him that we have our uniforms here, and our tools that we have to bring back, because-- because we couldn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to bring everything back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was afraid that he will tell us to open the package, because there were already situations from others, that if they found something which you are not allowed to do-- and especially when it came to Goeth, who was a-- who was a terrible man.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as shooting is concerned, he could shot every-- could shoot everybody in the morning when they counted all the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came out, and he shot somebody because he looked at him and somebody because he-- he looked aside from him, or whatever-- whatever his mood this day was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was no question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes people who came in, who smuggled something in, they hung and-- and he wanted everybody to be present at the same time when they hung him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was afraid what his next request would be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, he noticed that one of my packages sticking out-- was sticking out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked me, what-- what do you have in this packet?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
